data.description: Stunning and like a new construction home! Kitchen reveals beautiful cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances & large island. Master Suite displays a tray ceiling, HUGE 13x5 WIC, his/her marble vanities & 5ft shower! Fourth bedroom, large study, loft and full bath on 2nd floor! Screened in porch overlooking spacious backyard is perfect for relaxing and entertaining! Large corner lot, low HOA dues & no city taxes!
